        <Summary xml:lang="en">Control daemon, CLI and GUI for ASUS ROG laptops</Summary>
        <Description xml:lang="en">asusctl is a control daemon, CLI tools, and Slint-based GUI for
interacting with ASUS ROG laptops on Linux. It exposes platform
profile, keyboard LEDs (Aura), AniMe Matrix display, battery
charge limit, fan curves, and GPU MUX where supported.
</Description>
